main event: A sighting of a bright, white, star-like object was reported.
interesting points: The object was brighter than most stars but not as bright as the brightest star.,The object was about the size of typical stars in the sky but not as large as a bright planet.,The observation lasted approximately 2 minutes.,The report was submitted two years after the incident occurred.,There is speculation that the object could have been a light on an aircraft or a balloon.
